requisitionPacks.name: Spartan Rank 145 Officer Pack
requisitionPacks.description: Congratulations on reaching Spartan Rank 145!

requisitionPacks.name: Spartan Rank 146 Ascent Pack
requisitionPacks.description: You're almost at the pinnacle, now claim your REQ rewards.

requisitionPacks.name: Spartan Rank 147 Ascent Pack
requisitionPacks.description: There's only a few steps left. Here are some REQs to lighten your feet.

requisitionPacks.name: Spartan Rank 148 Ascent Pack
requisitionPacks.description: There's not much room at the top. Take these REQs and clear some room.

requisitionPacks.name: Spartan Rank 149 Trigger Puller Pack
requisitionPacks.description: Welcome to the world of Spartan special ops. Claim your REQs and get ready to introduce the Covenant to a world of pain.

requisitionPacks.name: Spartan Rank 150 Green Machine Pack
requisitionPacks.description: You came. You saw. You claimed some REQs from the torn wreckage.

requisitionPacks.name: Spartan Rank 151 Snake Eater Pack
requisitionPacks.description: Let's introduce these Insurrection rebels to a new world of pain with your new REQs.

requisitionPacks.name: Spartan Rank 152 Inheritor Pack
requisitionPacks.description: Enjoy the view from the top. Now, review your REQs and get ready for the next mission.
